t":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3501","Title":"福州"},{"Id":"14f167c71f164cea8b932e2cbb92df1e","Latitude":33.850774,"Longitude":115.785767,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3416","Title":"亳州"},{"Id":"9ce69aa1925541cd85d14c0227ec0a7e","Latitude":32.39986,"Longitude":119.419107,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN321","Title":"扬州"},{"Id":"e5c4b14016304fa7b40da3b44221b180","Latitude":34.210143,"Longitude":117.29235,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3203","Title":"徐州"},{"Id":"eb1cbee7ac6841dca0e9bc9c81cf9923","Latitude":34.420378,"Longitude":115.662798,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN4114","Title":"商丘"},{"Id":"d3605917692e44ed9bfdb3e3cdb2b91b","Latitude":34.802941,"Longitude":114.313904,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN4102","Title":"开封"}]}],"Markers":[{"Latitude":32.786776,"Longitude":119.462193,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN321084","Title":"高邮 (出生地)","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"bed499117ffb4b5eb387d4c1a09b8607\");'><span id='bed499117ffb4b5eb387d4c1a09b8607_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1028&endYear=1047')\">1028-1047年</a>，0-19岁</div><div id='bed499117ffb4b5eb387d4c1a09b8607' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1028&endYear=1041')\">1028-1041年</a>，居乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1042&endYear=1042')\">1042年</a>，通《易》、《书》、《春秋经》大义。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1043&endYear=1045')\">1043-1045年</a>，居乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1046&endYear=1046')\">1046年</a>，娶徐氏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1047&endYear=1047')\">1047年</a>，从海陵胡瑗游，入经社。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"6368ff2143a546858fcd6efd6a9cfc72\");'><span id='6368ff2143a546858fcd6efd6a9cfc72_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1061&endYear=1061')\">1061年</a>，33岁</div><div id='6368ff2143a546858fcd6efd6a9cfc72' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1061&endYear=1061')\">1061年</a>，自京归高邮，黄庭坚来谒，以女许庭坚。庭坚有诗《和答莘老见赠》<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"1c53500c32ed45dea8da5795f3e623f0\");'><span id='1c53500c32ed45dea8da5795f3e623f0_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1076&endYear=1078')\">1076-1078年</a>，48-50岁</div><div id='1c53500c32ed45dea8da5795f3e623f0' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1076&endYear=1076')\">1076年8月</a>，祖母丧，解官持服。在高邮。八月，访漳南道人昭庆于汤泉。与秦观有诗唱和。<span class='label'>作品：</span>过六合水亭怀裴博士。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">过六合水亭怀裴博士（宋·孙觉）<br />　　五言律诗　押歌韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->昔同裴博士，酌酒俯庭柯。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->晚岫潭潭碧，风池瑟瑟波。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->苍崖遗老没，白首故人过。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->转眄成陈迹，劳生可奈何<span class=\"small\">①</span>。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 同上书《过六合水亭怀裴博士次韵三首》其一　按：此系首唱，据清茆泮林《宋孙莘老年谱》，熙宁九年八月孙觉作此诗。参秦观诗存目。</span></div></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1076&endYear=1076')\">1076年8月</a>，在高邮。八月，访漳南道人昭庆于汤泉。与秦观有诗唱和。<span class='label'>作品：</span>初至汤泉。游龙洞。题阎求仁虚乐亭。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">初至汤泉（宋·孙觉）<br />　　五言律诗　押阳韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->川谷閟深阻，天时正莽苍。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->聊同不速客，来浴自然汤。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->茂宰蔼休政，道人栖净坊。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->恍如登十地，热恼顿清凉<span class=\"small\">①</span>。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 同上书卷七《次韵莘老初至汤泉二首》附</span></div></div>\r\n<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">游龙洞（宋·孙觉）<br />　　七言律诗　押青韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->侧径萦纡入杳冥，神镵鬼凿路岩扃。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->天悬乳石婴华盖，壁隐莓苔矗翠屏。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->九道寒江云外白，一池阳井雪中青。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->还同康乐登临海，可共羊何笔不停<span class=\"small\">①</span>。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 同上书《和莘老游龙洞》附</span></div></div>\r\n<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">题阎求仁虚乐亭（宋·孙觉）<br />　　七言律诗　押删韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->禅房幽构径弯环，噪鹊鸣鸠尽日闲。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->隐几冥濛超物表，画图彷佛见林间。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->褰帘云吐池中月，岸帻天横竹外山。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->秋兴已阑成丽句，板舆时此慰慈颜<span class=\"small\">①</span>。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 同上书同题三首其一　按：据题下原注此系觉首倡，参秦观诗存目。</span></div></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1076&endYear=1076')\">1076年10月</a>，在高邮。十月，王安石免，退居金陵，先生枉驾过之。王安石有《答孙莘老书。吴充同平章事，乞召还孙觉》等。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年</a>，在高邮。寄老庵成。黄庭坚代孙觉作赋《代孙莘老作寄老庵赋。》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年</a>，在高邮。<span class='label'>作品：</span>宝林禅院记。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1078&endYear=1078')\">1078年</a>，在高邮。黄庭坚过下邳阴侯庙，作诗示孙觉，孙觉改。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1078&endYear=1078')\">1078年</a>，在高邮。服除。与李公择、苏轼有诗唱和。<span class='label'>作品：</span>与施大夫赏花。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.39986,"Longitude":119.419107,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN321","Title":"扬州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"2278d89535404c65adff530c0b54ede0\");'><span id='2278d89535404c65adff530c0b54ede0_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1048&endYear=1048')\">1048年</a>，20岁</div><div id='2278d89535404c65adff530c0b54ede0' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1048&endYear=1048')\">1048年</a>，《春秋经社要义》成。是岁欧阳修知扬州，先生请益于欧阳公，公曰：“此无他术，唯勤读书而多为之，自工。世人患作文字少，又懒读书，每一篇出，即求过人，如此少有至者。疵病不必待人指摘，多作自见之。”孙书于座右。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"9ce69aa1925541cd85d14c0227ec0a7e\");'><span id='9ce69aa1925541cd85d14c0227ec0a7e_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年</a>，53岁</div><div id='9ce69aa1925541cd85d14c0227ec0a7e' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年</a>，徙知扬州，辞不赴。有书寄苏轼，秦观有书寄孙觉。<span class='label'>作品：</span>与苏先生简。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.802941,"Longitude":114.313904,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4102","Title":"开封","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"fcb781a9fd284b1b8c5a27c9c9cc5d14\");'><span id='fcb781a9fd284b1b8c5a27c9c9cc5d14_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1049')\">1049年</a>，21岁</div><div id='fcb781a9fd284b1b8c5a27c9c9cc5d14' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1049')\">1049年</a>，入京赴礼部应试，登进士第。未第时，讲学于郊馆别墅，甓社湖珠见，同舍崔伯易作《感珠赋》。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e7c985900c9549f2b0554cc17f5ee64f\");'><span id='e7c985900c9549f2b0554cc17f5ee64f_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1059&endYear=1060')\">1059-1060年</a>，31-32岁</div><div id='e7c985900c9549f2b0554cc17f5ee64f' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1059&endYear=1059')\">1059年</a>，编校昭文馆书籍。与王令唱和。王令有诗《杂诗效孙莘老》<span class='label'>作品：</span>杂诗呈逢源。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">杂诗呈逢原（宋·孙觉）<br />　　押养韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->鸿雁最知时，未逃罗与网。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->不能忘稻粱，千里安得往。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->鸣蜩腹空虚，见喙因其响。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->丹凤穴九霄，虞人常梦想<span class=\"small\">①</span>。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 宋王令《广陵集》卷一一</span></div></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1060&endYear=1060')\">1060年</a>，编校昭文馆书籍。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"8d3ac1122470497aa36a69112c2fcbc1\");'><span id='8d3ac1122470497aa36a69112c2fcbc1_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1063&endYear=1065')\">1063-1065年</a>，35-37岁</div><div id='8d3ac1122470497aa36a69112c2fcbc1' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1063&endYear=1063')\">1063年</a>，在京师。七月，与赵彦若、孙洙、曾巩等校定《陈书》，上之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1063&endYear=1063')\">1063年</a>，在京师。王惟熙嘉祐七年卒，明年葬，孙觉作墓志铭。<span class='label'>作品：</span>王惟熙墓志铭。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1064&endYear=1064')\">1064年</a>，在京师。某日，与滕胜道、钱醇老、孙巨源观花。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1065&endYear=1065')\">1065年</a>，在京师。弟孙览登进士第。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"161f02bd22f84c8b9f06b692cb7c7c50\");'><span id='161f02bd22f84c8b9f06b692cb7c7c50_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1067&endYear=1068')\">1067-1068年</a>，39-40岁</div><div id='161f02bd22f84c8b9f06b692cb7c7c50' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1067&endYear=1067')\">1067年</a>，直集贤院，擢右正言。<span class='label'>作品：</span>富贵二箴。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1068&endYear=1068')\">1068年1月</a>，正月，诏修《英宗实录》，与曾巩充检讨官。神宗将大革积弊，先生上言。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"25365019f00548b3ae11e85e64cc7f6e\");'><span id='25365019f00548b3ae11e85e64cc7f6e_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1068&endYear=1068')\">1068年</a>，40岁</div><div id='25365019f00548b3ae11e85e64cc7f6e' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1068&endYear=1068')\">1068年</a>，复右正言，以言事忤帝意，罢去。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"08ea97cb42d44c74bd4d1e7d799a563e\");'><span id='08ea97cb42d44c74bd4d1e7d799a563e_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1069&endYear=1070')\">1069-1070年</a>，41-42岁</div><div id='08ea97cb42d44c74bd4d1e7d799a563e' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1069&endYear=1069')\">1069年</a>，自通州召还，知谏院，同修起居注。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1069&endYear=1069')\">1069年</a>，以记注知谏院，同知贡举。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1069&endYear=1069')\">1069年</a>，改知审官院。疏论滕甫。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1069&endYear=1069')\">1069年</a>，知审官院。有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>论不当召对小臣询两府台阁人物奏。论不必每事遣使奏。乞以无灾为惧奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年2月</a>，知审官院。二月，韩琦请罢新法，为王安石所沮。先生疏论，不听。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"7c20aa9d0630405cbf72b80437eb4a2f\");'><span id='7c20aa9d0630405cbf72b80437eb4a2f_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1075&endYear=1075')\">1075年</a>，47岁</div><div id='7c20aa9d0630405cbf72b80437eb4a2f' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1075&endYear=1075')\">1075年</a>，改右司谏，值集贤院。秦观、僧道潜皆有《怀莘老司谏》诗。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"d3605917692e44ed9bfdb3e3cdb2b91b\");'><span id='d3605917692e44ed9bfdb3e3cdb2b91b_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1083&endYear=1090')\">1083-1090年</a>，55-62岁</div><div id='d3605917692e44ed9bfdb3e3cdb2b91b' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1083&endYear=1083')\">1083年</a>，入为太常少卿。秦观有诗《寄孙莘老少监》，参寥有诗《寄莘老》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1083&endYear=1083')\">1083年</a>，会李常为礼部侍郎，觉与李有隙，易为秘书少监。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1083&endYear=1083')\">1083年10月</a>，任秘书少监。弟孙览权京西路转运判官，更以京西提举官试右司员外郎。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1083&endYear=1083')\">1083年10月</a>，任秘书少监。有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞逐路委监司一员改刺逐州厢军奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1084&endYear=1084')\">1084年</a>，在秘书少监任.有寄墨苏轼，苏轼亦有诗《孙莘老寄墨》。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1084&endYear=1084')\">1084年7月</a>，在秘书少监任。弟孙览为河东转运使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1084&endYear=1084')\">1084年9月</a>，在秘书少监任。与叶祖洽、王仲修、钱长卿、韩宗古、赵彦若校定《算经》。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1085&endYear=1085')\">1085年3月</a>，在秘书少监任。三月，诏立延安郡王为皇太子，宫僚以司马光、吕公著及孙觉作之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1085&endYear=1085')\">1085年</a>，在秘书少监任。以秘书少监权知贡举。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1085&endYear=1085')\">1085年4月</a>，在秘书少监任。四月，兼侍讲。复寄墨东坡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1085&endYear=1085')\">1085年7月</a>，在秘书少监任。诏为右谏议大夫，赐三品服。黄庭坚和孙觉诗。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1085&endYear=1085')\">1085年</a>，在秘书少监任。有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞依天禧诏书奏。谥法当责任有司奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1085&endYear=1085')\">1085年9月</a>，供右谏议大夫职，兼侍讲。有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>上哲宗乞依六典备置谏官奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1085&endYear=1085')\">1085年11月丁巳</a>，在右谏议大夫职，兼侍讲。奏御史察官言事，乞令中丞等察举可言事者以闻。从之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>论御史察官言事奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年1月</a>，在右谏议大夫职，兼侍讲。正月，有奏议。<span class='label'>作品：</span>水旱灾变乞赐宰相罢黜奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年2月甲申</a>，在右谏议大夫职，兼侍讲。二月，疏论蔡确、韩缜。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞罢免蔡确韩缜奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年2月</a>，在右谏议大夫职，兼侍讲。蔡确自陈有功，孙觉复疏论之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>再乞罢免蔡确韩缜奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年2月</a>，在右谏议大夫职，兼侍讲。有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞令台谏先次上殿奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年2月</a>，在右谏议大夫职，兼侍讲。闰二月，诏与刘挚看详元丰八年命官诸色人赦状。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年2月</a>，在右谏议大夫职，兼侍讲。复疏论韩缜。<span class='label'>作品：</span>劾韩缜奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年2月</a>，在右谏议大夫职，兼侍讲。迁给事中，孙觉疏辞，乞留谏职。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞收还给事中新命且在谏职奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年</a>，在给事中职，兼侍讲。复疏论韩缜及章惇、张璪。<span class='label'>作品：</span>劾韩缜章惇张璪奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年</a>，在给事中职，兼侍讲。御史孙升奏请孙觉以给事中看详元丰八年以来断配人罪状。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年2月</a>，诏复为右谏议大夫，兼侍讲。疏论安焘。<span class='label'>作品：</span>劾安焘奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年3月</a>，在右谏议大夫职，兼侍讲。复疏论安焘。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞议经历付受官吏罪以正纪纲奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年3月</a>，在右谏议大夫职，兼侍讲。奏请刊定元丰编敕。<span class='label'>作品：</span>请刊定元丰编敕律令奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年</a>，在右谏议大夫职，兼侍讲。安焘免，孙觉疏谢，复乞罢韩缜。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞罢韩缜奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年4月</a>，在右谏议大夫职，兼侍讲。疏请赈济淮浙灾伤。<span class='label'>作品：</span>请体量灾伤赈济奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年4月壬辰</a>，诏为给事中兼侍讲。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年4月戊戌</a>，在给事中兼侍讲职。疏请看详囚徒，减降区断。<span class='label'>作品：</span>请旱灾宽减囚徒奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年4月</a>，在给事中兼侍讲职。<span class='label'>作品：</span>再乞罢免韩缜奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年5月戊辰</a>，在给事中兼侍讲职。诏与顾临、程颐看详修立太学条制。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年6月14日</a>，在给事中兼侍讲职。疏论将兵戊戍诸路。<span class='label'>作品：</span>请定将兵分路出戍奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年</a>，在给事中兼侍讲职。与胡宗愈、苏轼、范百禄疏留刘攽。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年</a>，在给事中兼侍讲职。与苏轼表荐郑侠为泉州教授。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年7月丙辰</a>，进吏部侍郎。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年11月乙卯</a>，任吏部侍郎兼侍讲。吕公著言中书侍郎未补入，孙觉、吕大防、李常皆可用，上然之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年</a>，任吏部侍郎兼侍讲。王安石卒，作文诔之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年</a>，任吏部侍郎兼侍讲。《尚书解义》成。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年</a>，任吏部侍郎兼侍讲。有奏。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞弃兰州奏。乞熙河选将如折氏世守奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1087&endYear=1087')\">1087年3月戊戌</a>，以吏部侍郎兼侍讲初领右选，寻改左选勘定选人额数。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1087&endYear=1087')\">1087年4月癸巳</a>，在吏部侍郎兼侍讲职。四月，与邓温伯、苏轼、李常、王存、胡宗愈疏留顾临于朝，不报。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1087&endYear=1087')\">1087年</a>，在吏部侍郎兼侍讲职。与苏轼、傅尧俞荐陈师道为俆州州学教授。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1087&endYear=1087')\">1087年</a>，在吏部侍郎兼侍讲职。孙览直龙图阁，权知秦州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1087&endYear=1087')\">1087年10月</a>，在吏部侍郎兼侍讲职。有奏。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞陕西官卖盐钞以救弊奏。<span class='inlineComment2'>（《全宋文》注时间为“绍圣二年十月”，是年孙觉已卒，误。时孙觉在秦州，应在“元祐二年”）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1087&endYear=1087')\">1087年11月庚申</a>，在吏部侍郎兼侍讲职。十一月，疏令御史纠举四方使者以闻，诏从之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞令御史台弹奏四方使者不法奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1087&endYear=1087')\">1087年</a>，在吏部侍郎兼侍讲职。有奏。<span class='label'>作品：</span>论帅臣当使便宜行事奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1088&endYear=1088')\">1088年1月乙丑</a>，在吏部侍郎兼侍讲职。春正月，诏与苏轼、孔文仲同知贡举。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1088&endYear=1088')\">1088年3月乙巳</a>，在吏部侍郎兼侍讲职。三月，与苏轼、孔文仲疏，乞去冗官之害。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1088&endYear=1088')\">1088年4月壬午</a>，擢御史中丞，兼侍讲。秦观有贺孙觉文。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1088&endYear=1088')\">1088年5月丙午72</a>，任御史中丞，兼侍讲。疏举欧阳棐自代。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1088&endYear=1088')\">1088年5月甲戌</a>，任御史中丞，兼侍讲。疏论胡宗愈。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1088&endYear=1088')\">1088年6月丙子</a>，任御史中丞，兼侍讲。疏请黄杲卿、黄颖除教导官，从之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1088&endYear=1088')\">1088年9月辛亥</a>，任御史中丞，兼侍讲。诏与苏轼、彭汝、张绩考试应贤良方正能直言极谏科举人。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1088&endYear=1088')\">1088年9月辛亥</a>，任御史中丞，兼侍讲。先生子子实端应制科，登进士。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1088&endYear=1088')\">1088年</a>，先生引疾求罢，诏为龙图阁直学士，提举醴泉观兼侍讲。刘攽有文《御史中丞孙觉可龙图阁直学士提举醴泉观依旧兼侍讲制》。黄庭坚送杖，李公择寄草元笔。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1088&endYear=1088')\">1088年</a>，提举醴泉观兼侍讲。《周易传》成。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1089&endYear=1089')\">1089年1月壬申</a>，春正月，诏免侍讲，依旧提举醴泉观，免朝参。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1089&endYear=1089')\">1089年5月</a>，在提举醴泉观任。五月，弟孙览为江淮荆浙等路发运副使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1089&endYear=1089')\">1089年</a>，孙觉请罢，求舒州灵山观以归。与秦观、黄庭坚有诗唱和。秦观诗《次韵莘老》，黄庭坚诗《答孙莘老见赠》、《又呈莘老》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1089&endYear=1089')\">1089年11月</a>，在提举醴泉观任。十一月，弟孙览权知桂州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1090&endYear=1090')\">1090年</a>，在提举醴泉观任。哲宗遣使存劳。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1090&endYear=1090')\">1090年2月3日</a>，二月丙申朔戊戌，孙觉卒。孙觉子子实时为郢州长寿县主簿，遂丁忧。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1090&endYear=1090')\">1090年2月3日</a>，三月，诏先生家钱五百缗，给葬事。秦少游有挽孙觉诗。子孙端归葬孙觉于广陵。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.624376,"Longitude":112.460033,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4103","Title":"洛阳","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"db73efcdee024983abd1d38388127a99\");'><span id='db73efcdee024983abd1d38388127a99_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1050')\">1049-1050年</a>，21-22岁</div><div id='db73efcdee024983abd1d38388127a99' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1049')\">1049年</a>，登进士第，为河南县主簿。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1050&endYear=1050')\">1050年</a>，主簿河南。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.82687,"Longitude":117.235447,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3401","Title":"合肥","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"d033c5c4facc4520a56f6ee6e0f05521\");'><span id='d033c5c4facc4520a56f6ee6e0f05521_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1051&endYear=1053')\">1051-1053年</a>，23-25岁</div><div id='d033c5c4facc4520a56f6ee6e0f05521' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1051&endYear=1051')\">1051年</a>，调合肥主簿。岁旱，州课民捕蝗输之官。觉以民艰食，当以蝗易米，是为除害而享利。守悦，推其说下之他县。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1052&endYear=1053')\">1052-1053年</a>，任合肥主簿。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"36db73f07c5d4e71984c0db1fb9567ff\");'><span id='36db73f07c5d4e71984c0db1fb9567ff_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1073&endYear=1074')\">1073-1074年</a>，45-46岁</div><div id='36db73f07c5d4e71984c0db1fb9567ff' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1073&endYear=1073')\">1073年</a>，春，由吴兴移知庐州，与苏轼唱和，苏轼有诗《次韵孙莘老见赠》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1073&endYear=1073')\">1073年4月</a>，与傅钦之晤刘攽于广陵。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1074&endYear=1074')\">1074年</a>，知庐州。以祖母丧，求解官，不可。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":29.721365,"Longitude":118.345096,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN341","Title":"黄山","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"29e4c8c0c9bf4d1e9e05c654cad58dee\");'><span id='29e4c8c0c9bf4d1e9e05c654cad58dee_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1054&endYear=1058')\">1054-1058年</a>，26-30岁</div><div id='29e4c8c0c9bf4d1e9e05c654cad58dee' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1054&endYear=1054')\">1054年</a>，合肥簿满秩，任宣州太平县令。与王令唱和。王令有诗《答孙莘老见寄》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1055&endYear=1055')\">1055年</a>，任宣州太平县令。与王令唱和，王令有《寄孙莘老》诗。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1056&endYear=1056')\">1056年</a>，任宣州太平县令。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1057&endYear=1057')\">1057年12月</a>，任宣州太平县令。有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>太平县县厅记。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1058&endYear=1058')\">1058年</a>，任宣州太平县令。与王安石唱和，王安石有《度麾岭寄莘老》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1058&endYear=1058')\">1058年3月</a>，任宣州太平县令。有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>众乐亭记。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":33.787173,"Longitude":119.267334,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN320826","Title":"涟水","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"9ca30fb2a8ee468c85efc7112460262e\");'><span id='9ca30fb2a8ee468c85efc7112460262e_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1062&endYear=1062')\">1062年</a>，34岁</div><div id='9ca30fb2a8ee468c85efc7112460262e' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1062&endYear=1062')\">1062年</a>，在涟水军，俞澹、黄庭坚从学。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.014847,"Longitude":120.639402,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN320509","Title":"吴江","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"0c090c90dd9a40e58820493aa91f693b\");'><span id='0c090c90dd9a40e58820493aa91f693b_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1066&endYear=1066')\">1066年</a>，38岁</div><div id='0c090c90dd9a40e58820493aa91f693b' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1066&endYear=1066')\">1066年</a>，出为吴江令。修垂虹桥。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.036519,"Longitude":120.586673,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3306","Title":"绍兴","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"851b396fb07743e085b8856602b1fdf5\");'><span id='851b396fb07743e085b8856602b1fdf5_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1068&endYear=1068')\">1068年</a>，40岁</div><div id='851b396fb07743e085b8856602b1fdf5' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1068&endYear=1068')\">1068年1月</a>，疏论邵亢，夺官两级，判越州。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.985237,"Longitude":120.900301,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3206","Title":"南通","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"47ff86a1c1414d3f924834f36a577273\");'><span id='47ff86a1c1414d3f924834f36a577273_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1068&endYear=1068')\">1068年</a>，40岁</div><div id='47ff86a1c1414d3f924834f36a577273' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1068&endYear=1068')\">1068年</a>，徙知通州。有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>过掘港营寨。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1068&endYear=1068')\">1068年</a>，知通州。有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>论所急者近效所勤者小数奏。论知人在务学奏。论自治以胜夷狄之患奏。论人主不宜有轻人臣之心奏。论君臣相疑之弊奏。论任贤使能之异奏。论取士之弊宜有改更奏。论治边之略奏。论果于用善断于去恶奏。论谏官贬秩不当再举其职奏。论人主当不为血气所变奏。论人主有高世之资求治之意在成之以学奏。乞定著内臣员数年未及四十不得入诸闺閤奏。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.900026,"Longitude":119.423498,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN341822","Title":"广德","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"1e2e6bd3a72c4f2684b5b54b4e92e379\");'><span id='1e2e6bd3a72c4f2684b5b54b4e92e379_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1071')\">1070-1071年</a>，42-43岁</div><div id='1e2e6bd3a72c4f2684b5b54b4e92e379' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年3月</a>，贬知广德军。张戬与台官王子韶论新法不便，乞首召还先生，不听。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年3月</a>，知广德军。有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>论条例司画一申明青苗事奏。论罢司马光枢密范镇封驳司不当奏。论青苗奏。辞免体量府界青苗钱奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1071&endYear=1071')\">1071年</a>，知广德军。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1071&endYear=1071')\">1071年8月</a>，知广德军，有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>婺源县建学记。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.899015,"Longitude":120.094566,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3305","Title":"湖州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"34c32873c926476296f8c823d9ae48bf\");'><span id='34c32873c926476296f8c823d9ae48bf_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1071&endYear=1073')\">1071-1073年</a>，43-45岁</div><div id='34c32873c926476296f8c823d9ae48bf' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1071&endYear=1071')\">1071年12月</a>，移知湖州，适大水，岁饥，觉赈仓廪，民甚德之。为屯田郎中俞汝奇作墓表。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1071&endYear=1071')\">1071年</a>，知湖州任。《春秋经解》成，先生自序。<span class='label'>作品：</span>春秋经解自序。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1072&endYear=1072')\">1072年</a>，知湖州，辑《吴兴诗集》。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1072&endYear=1072')\">1072年</a>，知湖州。作张氏《十咏图序》。<span class='label'>作品：</span>张维十咏图序。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1072&endYear=1072')\">1072年2月</a>，知湖州，作墨妙亭。苏轼作《孙莘老求墨妙亭》诗。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1072&endYear=1072')\">1072年12月</a>，判杭州，苏轼来遇，有诗寄孙觉，又赠七绝六首。黄庭坚、邵茂诚迎来。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1073&endYear=1073')\">1073年</a>，在湖州葺天庆观，作归雁亭。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.195688,"Longitude":119.431494,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3211","Title":"镇江","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"6021135813164cbda558a8cefa710d89\");'><span id='6021135813164cbda558a8cefa710d89_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1075&endYear=1075')\">1075年</a>，47岁</div><div id='6021135813164cbda558a8cefa710d89' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1075&endYear=1075')\">1075年10月</a>，十月辛亥，旋诏知润州。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.304566,"Longitude":120.589613,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3205","Title":"苏州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"642a644915c149ce9672e0b60f9cbf00\");'><span id='642a644915c149ce9672e0b60f9cbf00_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1079&endYear=1079')\">1079年</a>，51岁</div><div id='642a644915c149ce9672e0b60f9cbf00' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1079&endYear=1079')\">1079年</a>，起官知苏州，案治郑伋。自高邮知苏州，过邵伯亭，留诗斗野亭。与山谷、苏轼、少游有诗唱和。<span class='label'>作品：</span>题召伯斗野亭。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">题召伯斗野亭（宋·孙觉）<br />　　押庚韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->淮海无林邱，旷泽千里平。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->一渠闲防潴，物色故不清。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->老僧喜穿筑，北户延朱甍。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->檐楯斗杓落，帘帏河汉倾。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->平湖杳无涯，湛湛春波生。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->结缆嗟已晚，不见芙蓉城。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->尚想紫芡盘，明珠出新烹。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->平生有微尚，一舟聊寄行。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->遇胜辄偃蹇，霜须刷澄明。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->可待齿牙豁，归欤谢浮荣<span class=\"small\">①</span>。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 宋秦观《淮海集》卷三《和孙莘老题召伯斗野亭》附</span></div></div>\r\n<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":26.080447,"Longitude":119.302938,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3501","Title":"福州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"81e22b4f071d4d159193d5b5361aa2da\");'><span id='81e22b4f071d4d159193d5b5361aa2da_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1079&endYear=1080')\">1079-1080年</a>，51-52岁</div><div id='81e22b4f071d4d159193d5b5361aa2da' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1079&endYear=1079')\">1079年7月</a>，坐苏轼诗狱，徙知福州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1079&endYear=1079')\">1079年12月庚申</a>，知福州。御史舒亶言孙觉收受苏轼讥讽朝政文字，复坐罚铜。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1080&endYear=1080')\">1080年</a>，知福州。裁闽俗昏丧费，定为中制。募偿市易钱。秦观有《寄孙莘老学士简》，参寥有《寄福州太守孙莘老》诗。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1080&endYear=1080')\">1080年</a>，知福州。为越州祠堂记。<span class='label'>作品：</span>程给事祠堂记。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1080&endYear=1080')\">1080年</a>，知福州。夫人寿字君卒，子实遂丁忧。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1080&endYear=1080')\">1080年</a>，知福州。弟孙览以知尉氏县改司农寺主簿。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1080&endYear=1080')\">1080年9月</a>，知福州。作序文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>玄沙广录序。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":33.850774,"Longitude":115.785767,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3416","Title":"亳州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"14f167c71f164cea8b932e2cbb92df1e\");'><span id='14f167c71f164cea8b932e2cbb92df1e_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年</a>，53岁</div><div id='14f167c71f164cea8b932e2cbb92df1e' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年</a>，徙知亳州，辞不赴。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.210143,"Longitude":117.29235,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3203","Title":"徐州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e5c4b14016304fa7b40da3b44221b180\");'><span id='e5c4b14016304fa7b40da3b44221b180_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1082')\">1081-1082年</a>，53-54岁</div><div id='e5c4b14016304fa7b40da3b44221b180' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年</a>，徙知徐州。道经扬州，与秦观有交游。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年7月</a>，知徐州。有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>差补效庙监祭事奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年7月</a>，知徐州。为陈副使诗作跋。<span class='label'>作品：</span>陈副使诗跋。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年9月</a>，知徐州。为陈襄作墓志铭。<span class='label'>作品：</span>陈先生墓志铭。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1082&endYear=1082')\">1082年</a>，知徐州。释候门盗不诛，为例。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1082&endYear=1082')\">1082年</a>，知徐州。要昭玘为徐州教授，觉深礼之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1082&endYear=1082')\">1082年7月</a>，知徐州。请修城及官舍。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.420378,"Longitude":115.662798,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4114","Title":"商丘","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"eb1cbee7ac6841dca0e9bc9c81cf9923\");'><span id='eb1cbee7ac6841dca0e9bc9c81cf9923_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1082&endYear=1083')\">1082-1083年</a>，54-55岁</div><div id='eb1cbee7ac6841dca0e9bc9c81cf9923' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1082&endYear=1082')\">1082年7月</a>，诏知应天府。张舜民来遇。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1083&endYear=1083')\">1083年10月</a>，在应天府。十月，请修外城门及西桥等。<br /></div>"}],"Title":"孙觉 <span class='inlineComment2'>(1028-1090)</span>","Detail":"<p class='inlineComment2'>引用书目：茆泮林编，曹清华校点《宋孙莘老先生年谱》、曾枣庄、刘琳主编《全宋文》　录入整理：柯贞金</p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(0, 8, 115.961113, 32.262153, 8)\">0-33岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(0)\">高邮</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(1)\">扬州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(2)\">开封</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(3)\">洛阳</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(4)\">合肥</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(5)\">黄山</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(6)\">开封</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(7)\">高邮</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(8, 12, 117.476653, 32.908894, 8)\">34-40岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(8)\">涟水</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(9)\">开封</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(10)\">吴江</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(11)\">开封</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(12, 16, 117.6071025, 32.41973, 8)\">40-42岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(12)\">绍兴</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(13)\">开封</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(14)\">南通</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(15)\">开封</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(16, 20, 117.204235, 32.850978, 8)\">42-47岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(16)\">广德</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(17)\">湖州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(18)\">合肥</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(19)\">开封</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(20, 29, 117.4517585, 30.441694, 7)\">47-62岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(20)\">镇江</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(21)\">高邮</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(22)\">苏州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(23)\">福州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(24)\">亳州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(25)\">扬州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(26)\">徐州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(27)\">商丘</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(28)\">开封</a></p>"}]}